345
00:29:03,300 --> 00:29:04,580
Why gerberas?

346
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:07,910
Shouldn't you be growing roses?

347
00:29:10,140 --> 00:29:11,190
It's because of the blooming season.

348
00:29:13,230 --> 00:29:14,540
Gerberas bloom late.

349
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:19,820
