352
00:29:32,190 --> 00:29:33,990
You are my last woman.

353
00:29:45,670 --> 00:29:46,510
Got it.

354
00:29:56,580 --> 00:29:57,780
Xiao Han.

355
00:29:58,860 --> 00:29:59,950
