356
00:30:01,710 --> 00:30:02,620
What's wrong?

357
00:30:05,780 --> 00:30:07,100
Does it hurt here?

358
00:30:10,580 --> 00:30:11,270
It's okay.

359
00:30:12,100 --> 00:30:13,030
It should be altitude sickness.

360
00:30:14,190 --> 00:30:15,540
