365
00:30:43,030 --> 00:30:44,030
My head.

366
00:30:44,540 --> 00:30:45,750
I need oxygen.

367
00:30:47,340 --> 00:30:49,060
I need oxygen. Help me.

368
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:52,030
