388
00:32:58,540 --> 00:32:59,340
It's perfect for her.

389
00:32:59,470 --> 00:33:00,470
What did your uncle say?

390
00:33:00,470 --> 00:33:01,380
No.

391
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:03,470
He said it's not

392
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:04,510
