462
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:38,910
Our customs

463
00:35:38,990 --> 00:35:40,790
are different from
those of your big city.

464
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:42,180
Nobody gives money.

465
00:35:42,350 --> 00:35:44,260
They give items in return.

466
00:35:44,830 --> 00:35:46,700
